  1	# Severity Summary Toggle Implementation Guide
  2	
  3	## Overview
  4	This guide documents the complete implementation of the two-button toggle approach for the severity summary component, including all CSS, HTML structure, and JavaScript functionality.
  5	
  6	## HTML Structure
  7	
  8	### Current Implementation
  9	```html
 10	<!-- Severity Summary Component -->
 11	<div class="severity-summary-component" id="severitySummary">
 12	    <!-- Collapsed label -->
 13	    <span class="severity-summary-collapsed-label">show severity</span>
 14	    
 15	    <!-- Header with toggle button -->
 16	    <div class="severity-summary-header-wrapper">
 17	        <h2 class="severity-summary-header">severity summary</h2>
 18	        <!-- Toggle button for expanded state -->
 19	        <button class="severity-summary-toggle severity-summary-toggle-expanded" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="severity-summary-content">
 20	            <i data-lucide="circle-chevron-up"></i>
 21	        </button>
 22	        <!-- Toggle button for collapsed state -->
 23	        <button class="severity-summary-toggle severity-summary-toggle-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="severity-summary-content">
 24	            <i data-lucide="circle-chevron-down"></i>
 25	        </button>
 26	    </div>
 27	    
 28	    <!-- Collapsible Content -->
 29	    <div class="severity-summary-content" id="severity-summary-content">
 30	        <div class="severity-boxes-row">
 31	            <!-- Severity boxes here -->
 32	        </div>
 33	    </div>
 34	</div>
 35	```
 36	
 37	## CSS Specifications
 38	
 39	### Component Container
 40	```css
 41	.severity-summary-component {
 42	    position: relative;
 43	    width: 100%;
 44	    display: flex;
 45	    flex-direction: column;
 46	    padding: 16px 24px 0 24px; /* Match filter-counter padding */
 47	    margin-top: -19px; /* Move up by 19px (14px + 5px) */
 48	    box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding in width calculation */
 49	}
 50	```
 51	
 52	### Header Wrapper
 53	```css
 54	.severity-summary-header-wrapper {
 55	    position: relative;
 56	    width: 100%;
 57	    display: flex;
 58	    align-items: center;
 59	    margin-bottom: 7px;
 60	    overflow: visible; /* Ensure buttons aren't clipped */
 61	}
 62	```
 63	
 64	### Header Text
 65	```css
 66	.severity-summary-header {
 67	    font-family: "jaf-bernino-sans-comp", sans-serif;
 68	    font-weight: 800;
 69	    font-style: normal;
 70	    font-size: 24pt; /* Reduced from 30pt to match demo */
 71	    color: rgba(37, 53, 65, 0.9);
 72	    margin: 0; /* Reset all margins */
 73	    text-transform: lowercase;
 74	    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
 75	    flex: 1; /* Take available space */
 76	    text-align: left;
 77	}
 78	```
 79	
 80	### Toggle Button Base Styles
 81	```css
 82	.severity-summary-toggle {
 83	    position: absolute; /* Back to absolute for better control */
 84	    right: 0px; /* Moved 8px to the right (was 8px) */
 85	    top: 50%; /* Center vertically */
 86	    transform: translateY(-50%); /* Perfect vertical center */
 87	    width: 28px;
 88	    height: 28px;
 89	    background: none;
 90	    border: none;
 91	    cursor: pointer;
 92	    display: flex;
 93	    align-items: center;
 94	    justify-content: center;
 95	    z-index: 10;
 96	    transition: all 300ms ease;
 97	}
 98	
 99	.severity-summary-toggle svg {
100	    color: #A8AEB3 !important;
101	    stroke: #A8AEB3 !important;
102	    fill: none !important;
103	    width: 28px;
104	    height: 28px;
105	    transition: all 300ms ease;
106	    display: block;
107	}
108	
109	.severity-summary-toggle:hover svg {
110	    color: #F26419 !important;
111	    stroke: #F26419 !important;
112	}
113	```
114	
115	### Collapsed Button Specific Styles
116	```css
117	/* Hide collapsed button by default */
118	.severity-summary-toggle-collapsed {
119	    display: none; /* Hidden by default */
120	    width: 15px;
121	    height: 15px;
122	    padding: 1px; /* Center the 13px icon in 15px button */
123	    z-index: 20; /* Higher z-index */
124	    background: none;
125	    /* Position it differently since absolute positioning */
126	    right: -2px !important; /* Moved 6px to the right (was 4px) */
127	}
128	
129	.severity-summary-toggle-collapsed svg {
130	    width: 10.5px !important;
131	    height: 10.5px !important;
132	    stroke-width: 2.5 !important; /* Thicker stroke for better visibility */
133	    color: #A8AEB3 !important;
134	    stroke: #A8AEB3 !important;
135	    fill: none !important;
136	    display: block !important;
137	}
138	```
