183	### Content Container
184	```css
185	.severity-summary-content {
186	    overflow: hidden;
187	    transition: all 300ms ease;
188	    transform-origin: top;
189	    width: 100%;
190	    padding: 0; /* No padding - handled by children */
191	    margin: 0;
192	}
